reviewText: Great DVD! If you like Steve or Chet this is for you!
I bought this item though I love the song "SAILS" it's a great song. The rest of the album is really good but not an favoritealbum, it dosen't matter 'cause "SAILS" is worth every dollar...
This is one of the best instructional DVD I have ever used. Very easy to follow and Mr. Wariner really gives you the theory behind his technical style.
